{
  "texts": [
    "Because the maximum number of tokens for the text-davinci-003 model is 4,097, we excluded all cases whose facts sections exceeded this number of tokens (using OpenAI's Tokenizer tool to calculate the number of tokens) (OpenAI 2023c).",
    "This resulted in the exclusion of 50 cases.",
    "We also excluded any administrative SEC cases (n = 9).",
    "There were two pairs of cases which were filed separately, but with nearly identical facts sections, due to lawyers having chosen not to join the defendants.",
    "For each of the two pairs, we chose to include whichever case had a more detailed facts section in our final data set and excluded the other."
  ]
}